      "text": [
        " أَمِيرُ اَلْمُؤْمِنِينَ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ لِشُرَيْحٍ : \"يَا شُرَيْحُ قَدْ جَلَسْتَ مَجْلِساً مَا جَلَسَهُ إِلاَّ نَبِيٌّ أَوْ وَصِيٌّ نَبِيٍّ أَوْ شَقِيٌّ \"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3223 - Commander of the Faithful Imam Ali ibn Abi Talib (as) said to Shurayh:\n\"O Shurayh, you have sat in a position that none has sat in except a prophet, the executor of a prophet, or a wretched person.\""
        ]
      }
